Class QueryBuilder

java.lang.Object
  com.mcgath.regbrowser.QueryBuilder
Direct Known Subclasses:
QueryBuilderDbpedia, QueryBuilderP2, QueryBuilderPronom, QueryBuilderUDFR
public abstract class QueryBuilder
extends java.lang.Object

Class to construct a query from the fields of a QueryWindow. It's a superclass for query builders for specific repositories.

checkFields

public QueryBuilder.QueryCheckCode checkFields()
Check if the fields are suitable for a query. There needs to be at least one non-blank one, and there can't be characters that would mess up a regular expression. Returns a QueryCheckCode.
